schools.name: Deer Park High School - North Campus

data.description: Discover this residence in the heart of DPISD! Step into your retreat as you explore the enchanting backyard, a sanctuary boasting a glistening in-ground pool with a slide. Revel in outdoor living with a covered patio and a pool house, meticulously reconstructed, including a mini split AC/heat, refrigerator, bathroom with shower, and sink. A thoughtfully designed split floor plan awaits, adorned with carpeting replaced in bedrooms 2022, while ceramic tiles are in the remaining spaces. The primary suite indulges with dual walk-in closets, catering to his and her storage needs. Experience comfort year-round with the installed AC unit in 21, ensuring optimal climate control. Essential updates include a roof replacement in 2016, a water heater upgrade in 24, and a garbage disposal in 23. Granite countertops adorn the kitchen, complemented by a comprehensive sprinkler system covering both front and backyards, promising convenience and ease in maintaining the landscape.
